data.description:
Step into the warmth of this delightful single-family duplex home, perfectly situated in a sought-after neighborhood. This home embraces a cozy atmosphere with 3 bedrooms and 1 1/2 baths, creating a comfortable haven for everyday living.

As you enter, a welcoming living space sets the tone for relaxation and gatherings. The Kitchen becomes the heart of the home, inviting you to create culinary delights and share memorable meals with loved ones.

Discover three bedrooms filled with natural light, providing versatile spaces for rest, work or play. The primary bedroom is a retreat of its own. The remaining bedrooms offer flexibility for your unique needs, be it a guest room, home office, or a cozy nook.

Step out front to a nice patio offering an outdoor space to relax and take in the fresh air. The duplex setting ensures a sense of community, creating a friendly and neighborly atmosphere.

Come and experience the charm of this duplex - a home that resonates with your lifestyle and beckons you to create your own story within its walls. Schedule a showing today and envision the possibilities that await you.
